Class LocManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • LocManager
  • public class LocManager
extends java.lang.Object
    LocaManager class represents the manager of game objects' Locations. Other classes - Ghost, Pacman, Stage - use this class to update and refer to locations of game objects.
    Version:
    2021. 5. 27.
    Author:
    Bedri, Richie
